OL,3,CDouble killer found guilty of
OL,4,Cmurdering neighbour after release from
OL,5,Cprison
OL,7,FA convicted double killer has been
OL,8,Ffound guilty of the murder of his
OL,9,Fneighbour following his release from
OL,10,Fprison.
OL,12,FBrian Whitelock, 57, attacked
OL,13,Fneighbour Wendy Buckney, 71, with a
OL,14,Fkitchen knife, a broken table leg and
OL,15,Fwooden shelving during a sustained
OL,16,Fassault in her own home.
OL,18,FThe bloodstained and naked pensioner
OL,19,Fwas discovered in the living room of
OL,20,Fher home in Clydach, near Swansea, on
OL,21,F23 August, 2022.
