OL,7,FSwansea Crown Court heard Whitelock
OL,8,Fhad been jailed for life in 2001 for
OL,9,Fmurder and manslaughter and released
OL,10,Ffrom prison in 2018.
OL,12,FHe was convicted by a jury who
OL,13,Fdeliberated for less than 30 minutes
OL,14,Ffollowing a two-week trial.
OL,16,FFollowing the guilty verdict,
OL,17,FWhitelock shouted at the jury from the
OL,18,Fdock and had to be escorted from the
OL,19,Fcourtroom.
