OL,7,FHe said: "I hope you all suffer a
OL,8,Fbrain injury, I hope you all suffer a
OL,9,Fbrain injury. I hope you all suffer
OL,10,Fwhat I went through. You are all bang
OL,11,Fout of order."
OL,13,FMr Justice Griffiths adjourned the
OL,14,Fcase for sentencing on December 20.
OL,16,FHe told the jury: "I apologise for
OL,17,Fthat disgraceful behaviour, you can be
OL,18,Fquite certain that Mr Whitelock is in
OL,19,Fa safe place from whence he can do you
OL,20,Fno harm."
