OL,7,FMr Rees said Ms Buckney must have
OL,8,F"suffered greatly" at the hands of
OL,9,FWhitelock before her death, having
OL,10,Fsustained multiple stab injuries,
OL,11,Fsharp force injuries and blunt force
OL,12,Finjuries.
OL,14,FHe added: "You will also hear evidence
OL,15,Fof sexual assault upon her ` whether
OL,16,Fthis was done by the defendant before,
OL,17,Fduring or after his attack upon her is
OL,18,Fimpossible, forensically, to say."
