OL,7,FWhitelock, who represented himself
OL,8,Fduring the trial, told jurors he had
OL,9,Fno memory of the incident and was
OL,10,Fsuffering from a brain injury at the
OL,11,Ftime after he slipped over while out
OL,12,Ffishing.
OL,14,FIn a statement, Ms Buckney's family
OL,15,Fdescribed her as a "much loved, sister
OL,16,Fand aunty".
