OL,7,FThey said: "Today's verdict brings
OL,8,Fsome measure of justice for Wendy, who
OL,9,Fwas taken from us far too soon. While
OL,10,Fnothing can bring her back, we are
OL,11,Fgrateful that the truth has been heard.
OL,13,F"Wendy was a very much loved, sister
OL,14,Fand aunty whose kindness, laughter and
OL,15,Fspirit touched the lives of so many.
OL,16,FOur lives will never be the same
OL,17,Fwithout her, but we will continue to
OL,18,Fhonour her memory every day.
