OL,7,F"This has been a painful and
OL,8,Fheartbreaking journey for our family.
OL,9,FWe thank everyone who has supported us
OL,10,Fduring this incredibly difficult time
OL,11,Fand we ask for privacy as we continue
OL,12,Fto grieve and heal in the wake of this
OL,13,Ftragedy."
OL,15,FThey also thanked the prosecution team
OL,16,Ffor their "dedication and commitment",
OL,17,Fand for bringing "the truth to light".
