OL,7,FDetective Chief Inspector Matt Davies
OL,8,Fsaid: "We are pleased to hear of the
OL,9,Fguilty verdict, concluding what has
OL,10,Fbeen a thorough investigation into
OL,11,FBrian Whitelock's senseless murder of
OL,12,Fhis defenceless victim.
OL,14,F"The family of Wendy Buckney have been
OL,15,Fthrough a terrible and traumatising
OL,16,Fordeal due to Brian Whitelock's
OL,17,Factions. With this verdict and the
OL,18,Fupcoming sentencing, I hope that they
OL,19,Ffeel some closure."
